* Introduction
  - Provide an overview of the feature being requested. Providing context and what the goal of the feature is
  - Expected Delivery Dates of the feature should be listed when possible
* Feature Description
  - Detailed description of the feature being requested, breaking down the entirety of the structure and/or process.
  - Be as detailed as possible while maintaining a clear goal to request an enhancement. Remember other documents can be worked on to provide context
* Scope - Permissions
  - Provide details and usage of the feature based on across the portals being utilized for this enhancement
* Scope - Dependencies
  - List out any module that is going to be tied in for the enhancement being requested. Providing how the module will be used.
* Supporting Documentation
  - Provide an outline of how testing will be handled and processed for the enhancement.
* Deliverables
  - Inclusion of the documents that either will or have relations to this enhancement. Providing either the planned target dates or context of aspects of the enhancement.
  - Provide details and targets for the enhancement, providing dates on when documents will be provided and/or released.
